00:41:35.449 --> 00:41:39.269
&gt;&gt;&gt; Hi, Steve.
Thanks for coming today.

00:41:39.269 --> 00:41:43.910
You mentioned that the expenditure of your
department has decreased during your tenure.

00:41:43.910 --> 00:41:50.390
But what Meg Whitman is saying is that it's
increased by, like, 14%, I believe.

00:41:50.390 --> 00:41:52.710
What do you say to that?
&gt;&gt;Steve Poizner: She's wrong.

00:41:52.710 --> 00:41:57.630
And she's very misleading.
Her negative attacks are ugly, nasty, false.

00:41:57.630 --> 00:42:01.369
Shame on her.
If you see her out there, you tell her.

00:42:01.369 --> 00:42:04.460
[ Laughter ]
